summary: Greg Andersen calls Julie D'Arcane to ask for help with his hacky sacks. The sacks have been up on the balcony since 1988.
suggested_actions: Confirm the date and time of Greg Andersen's visit to retrieve the hacky sacks to ensure availability.
Check the condition of the hacky sacks and the balcony area to prepare for Greg's arrival.
Follow up with Greg after the visit to ensure he successfully retrieved the hacky sacks and address any further needs.
